+# Action catalog
+
+This catalog defines the minimum resolution and promotion actions expected in the exceptions lake.
+
+## Resolution scopes
+
+- `case`
+- `rule`
+- `taxonomy`
+- `ontology`
+- `governance`
+
+## Common action types
+
+### Case resolution
+- `fix_case_record`
+- `request_missing_evidence`
+- `close_as_noise`
+
+### Rule resolution
+- `adjust_threshold`
+- `add_override_guardrail`
+- `change_transition_rule`
+
+### Taxonomy resolution
+- `add_alias`
+- `split_category`
+- `merge_category`
+- `add_missing_label`
+
+### Ontology resolution
+- `add_entity_type`
+- `add_relation_type`
+- `retire_relation_type`
+- `change_cardinality`
+
+### Governance resolution
+- `escalate_authority`
+- `change_policy`
+- `change_approval_path`
+- `record_executive_exception`
+
+## Promotion targets
+
+- `rule`
+- `taxonomy`
+- `ontology`
+- `policy`
+- `authority`
+
+## Design note
+Keep local resolution distinct from promoted learning.
+
+The same exception may resolve locally while still promoting a broader change later.
